However, avoid combining three or more ingredients, especially mixing magical and mundane types, as this frequently results in 'overcomplicated' items with significantly lower or even negative values. Also, refrain from filtering items that are already extracts or 'poorly-filtered' as it typically has no benefit or worsens them.
